{"title":"奶牛代理商 XI","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3201","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小徐是USACO中国区的奶牛代理商，专门销售质优价廉的“FJ”牌奶牛。</p>\n<p>有一天，她正在卖奶牛，突然觉得很孤单，想把她的朋友接来。</p>\n<p>可这要花一大笔钱。</p>\n<p>她有N个牛棚，想让你帮她重新围一块地，包含所有牛棚，且是凸多边形（否则奶牛会撞墙角）</p>\n<p>她现在经济很困难，不用你关心省下的地能卖多少钱，只要能让围栏最短，花最少的钱。</p>\n<p>请你计算围栏的最短长度。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N</p>\n<p>每个牛棚的坐标（整数）</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>最短长度（保留2位小数）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n<p>0 3</p>\n<p>3 0</p>\n<p>0 0</p>\n<p>1 1</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>10.24</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N&lt;=1000</p>\n<p>|X|，|Y|《=500.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}